            "headline": "Intercont (Cayman) Ltd prices IPO at $7/share, offering 1.5M Ordinary Shares, expecting $10.5M gross proceeds, to trade on Nasdaq as \"NCT\".",
            "id": "8ffb4602-6c48-4ad8-987d-22380cb5e26c",
            "is_major": false,
            "source": "GlobeNewswire",
            "source_type": "news",
            "summary": "Intercont (Cayman) Limited, a global shipping company venturing into seaborne pulping operations, has disclosed the pricing details of its initial public offering (IPO) on March 27, 2025. The offering consists of 1,500,000 ordinary shares valued at $7.00 per share. This pricing is anticipated to raise $10,500,000 in total gross proceeds for the company, excluding underwriting discounts and other expenses related to the offering. The Ordinary Shares have received approval for listing on the Nasdaq Capital Market and are set to start trading on March 28, 2025, under the symbol \u201cNCT\u201d.",
